{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"MouseEvent.which","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/conflicting/Web/API/UIEvent/which","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/UIEvent\"><code>UIEvent</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Constructor</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/UIEvent/UIEvent\"><code>UIEvent()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>属性</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/UIEvent/detail\"><code>detail</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/UIEvent/sourceCapabilities\"><code>sourceCapabilities</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/UIEvent/view\"><code>view</code></a></li><li><em><code>which</code></em></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>方法</summary><ol><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/UIEvent/initUIEvent\"><code>initUIEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Events</summary><ol><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/UIEvent/initUIEvent\"><code>initUIEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>继承</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Event\"><code>Event</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>\n\n<p></p><div class=\"notecard warning\" id=\"sect1\"><p><strong>非标准:</strong> 该特性是非标准的，请尽量不要在生产环境中使用它！</p></div><p></p>\n\n<p>只读属性 <strong>MouseEvent.which</strong> 显示了鼠标事件是由哪个鼠标按键被按下所触发的。其他获得该信息的标准属性是 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/MouseEvent/button\"><code>MouseEvent.button</code></a> 与 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/MouseEvent/buttons\"><code>MouseEvent.buttons</code></a> 。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"语法","title":"语法","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\">var buttonPressed = instanceOfMouseEvent.which\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"返回值","title":"返回值","isH3":true,"content":"<p>表示一个特定按键的数字：</p>\n\n<ul>\n <li><code>0</code>: 无</li>\n <li><code>1</code>: 左键</li>\n <li><code>2</code>: 中间滚轮（如果有的话）</li>\n <li><code>3</code>: 右键</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>如果鼠标被设置为适用于左利手人士使用，那么引发的动作恰好相反。在这种情况下，该值应该从右往左看。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"规范","title":"规范","isH3":false,"content":"<p>无规范定义该属性。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"browser_compatibility","title":"浏览器兼容性","isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect2\"><strong><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/browser-compat-data\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">We're converting our compatibility data into a machine-readable JSON format</a></strong>.\n            This compatibility table still uses the old format,\n            because we haven't yet converted the data it contains.\n            <strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Structures/Compatibility_tables\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Find out how you can help! (en-US)</a></strong></div>\n\n<div class=\"htab\" id=\"sect3\">\n    <a id=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\" name=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\"></a>\n    <ul>\n        <li class=\"selected\"><a href=\"#compat-desktop\">Desktop</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"#compat-mobile\">Mobile</a></li>\n    </ul>\n</div><p></p>\n\n<div id=\"compat-desktop\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Feature</th>\n   <th>Edge</th>\n   <th>Firefox (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>Chrome</th>\n   <th>Internet Explorer</th>\n   <th>Opera</th>\n   <th>Safari</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Basic support</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td>1.0 (1.7 or earlier)<sup>[1]</sup></td>\n   <td>1.0</td>\n   <td>9.0</td>\n   <td>5.0</td>\n   <td>1.0</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<div id=\"compat-mobile\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Feature</th>\n   <th>Edge</th>\n   <th>Firefox Mobile (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>Android</th>\n   <th>IE Mobile</th>\n   <th>Opera Mobile</th>\n   <th>Safari Mobile</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Basic support</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td>1.0 (1) [1]</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<p>[1] 在 <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/mousemove_event\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">mousemove (en-US)</a></code> 事件对象上，&nbsp;<code>which</code> 属性被错误地设定为&nbsp;<code>1</code>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://bugzilla.mozilla.org/show_bug.cgi?id=1048294\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">bug&nbsp;1048294</a>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"相关内容","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/MouseEvent\"><code>MouseEvent</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"语法","id":"语法"},{"text":"规范","id":"规范"},{"text":"浏览器兼容性","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"相关内容","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"只读属性 MouseEvent.which 显示了鼠标事件是由哪个鼠标按键被按下所触发的。其他获得该信息的标准属性是 MouseEvent.button 与 MouseEvent.buttons 。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"MouseEvent.which","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/conflicting/web/api/uievent/which","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/conflicting/web/api/uievent/which/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/conflicting/Web/API","title":"指数"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/conflicting/Web/API/UIEvent/which","title":"MouseEvent.which"}],"pageTitle":"MouseEvent.which | MDN","noIndexing":true}}